{
  "stem": "2966.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a little window looking out on what was going on, and It's really indescribable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans formed or they opened up an orphanage for little children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a few hundred children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, they took all those children-- take them away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to bring, from all around-- because we were right on the main street, looking at the main thoroughfare of the town-- they used to bring Jews with long beards, with the tallis on it from the prayer, taking them on the trucks and taking them to the-- pulling and beating and-- and yelling and screaming.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like a nightmare that will never go away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that lasted, like I said, two days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then we went back home, and we thought it was all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when it started again, we ran back to that store, through the fields.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were very lucky that we got there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we survived that biggest action.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they started talking about a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Up to that time, we still lived in our homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some of the homes, of the very big homes, were taken away for the German officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But most of the people that-- the average home was not that elaborate for them to live on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started talking about ghettos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in our town, they formed two ghettos in two different parts of the town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ghettos was not enclosed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no walls around it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because of the industry-- of the oil industry-- our people still could walk through the town, as long as they had their band on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
